{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020-03-29-export-ssm-to-shell/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ohmybuck"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"02908827-b6b0-5f94-8040-3e5c38ef7de6","excerpt":"This gets any params set in AWS SSM and exports it to the running shell.","html":"<p>This gets any params set in AWS SSM and exports it to the running shell.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token shebang important\">#!/bin/bash</span>\n\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">VAR_ENV_FILE</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$1</span>\"</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">VAR_SSM_PREFIX</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$2</span>\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># To use:</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># . export-ssm-to-shell.sh &lt;VAR_ENV_FILE> &lt;SSM_PREFIX></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># EXAMPLE</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#   . ./export-ssm-to-shell.sh .env.example /application/project/environment/</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> -z <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$VAR_ENV_FILE</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">then</span>\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"It appears you did not specify a file with the list of variables to fetch\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\". ./export-ssm-to-shell.sh .env.example /application/project/environment/\"</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exit</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fi</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> -z <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$VAR_SSM_PREFIX</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">then</span>\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"It appears you did not specify an SSM prefix\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\". ./export-ssm-to-shell.sh .env.example /application/project/environment/\"</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exit</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fi</span>\n\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">LIST_ENV_VARS</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">grep</span> -v <span class=\"token string\">'^#'</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$VAR_ENV_FILE</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sed</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"s/=.*//\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">xargs</span> -I <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$VAR_SSM_PREFIX</span>{}\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">tr</span> <span class=\"token string\">'<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\n\">\\n</span>'</span> <span class=\"token string\">' '</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">LIST_ENV_VAR_WITH_VALUES</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>aws ssm get-parameters --names <span class=\"token punctuation\">$(</span>echo <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$LIST_ENV_VARS</span>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>\n  jq -r <span class=\"token string\">\".Parameters[] | (.Name + <span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\&quot;\">\\\"</span>=<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\&quot;\">\\\"</span> + .Value)\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\n\">\\n</span>[EXPORT STARTING]\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$LIST_ENV_VAR_WITH_VALUES</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">read</span> LINE_ENV_VAR<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">do</span>\n  <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">CLEAN_ENV_VAR</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$LINE_ENV_VAR</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">sed</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"s|<span class=\"token variable\">$VAR_SSM_PREFIX</span>||\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$CLEAN_ENV_VAR</span>\"</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"[EXPORT SUCCESS]: <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> $LINE_ENV_VAR <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sed</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"s/=.*//\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">done</span>\n\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\n\">\\n</span>[EXPORT COMPLETED]\"</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Export SSM to shell","date":"March 29, 2020","description":"Export SSM to shell"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020-03-29-export-ssm-to-shell/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-03-29-export-vars-to-ssm/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Export vars to SSM","draft":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-04-15-slack-notifications-circle-ci/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Slack Notifications from Circle CI","draft":null}}}}}